# GitHub user and org profile URLs (often 404 due to deleted/renamed accounts)
https://github.com/[^/]+$

# LinkedIn (always returns 999 for bots)
https://www.linkedin.com/

# Conference registration (blocks bots)
https://reg.conf.posit.co/

# Relative paths - lychee misresolves these to site root, but they work in Hugo
# Images
http://localhost:1313/.*\.(png|jpg|jpeg|gif|svg|webp)$
# R Markdown artifacts
http://localhost:1313/.*_files/
